{"tid":662850,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島四日三夜行程求評","createTime":"2018-05-12T18:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T17:23:23.000Z","uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7053efd964fb068ae87ae6c8c3d022ce89de8856","tid":662850,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:45:12.000Z","msg":"話說下個月去日本交流 完左有四日三夜既時間玩 但我又未去過鹿兒島 所以想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三人行 <br />\n<br />\nDay 1高千穗峽 高千穗天空鐵路 <br />\n<br />\nDay 2指宿玉手箱 砂樂 /healthy land露天風呂  長崎鼻 池田湖 之後jr番鹿兒島<br />\n<br />\nDay 3隼人之風 霧島神宮 神話之里 之後返國分 JR返鹿兒島中央 屋台村<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 9行 12點左右到機場<br />\n<br />\n頭一日stay高千穗 之後兩日會住鹿兒島 所以都想問下有咩住宿推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212c5045a55d85c805d029e84d5794389aff783a","tid":662850,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:50:58.000Z","msg":"補番先 day1我地會由鹿兒島出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590d116958c054d109ee958f058ba56551552e56","tid":662850,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a7a27355361bb8cc4c3caa1626c4b3ff3445e2","tid":662850,"uid":125109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"首先利申 未試過宮崎自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔知你啲行李會點處理<br />\n<br />\n直覺上覺得day 2同day 3調轉會好啲<br />\n<br />\n指宿果邊如果唔自駕<br />\n而係搭巴士遊曬幾個景點<br />\n可能要10點幾就到指宿<br />\n如果第二日係宮崎去鹿兒島 再去指宿<br />\n唔知你啲交通配唔配合到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b140b97c99026f33914ec8e801f87c7547daebb","tid":662850,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a7a27355361bb8cc4c3caa1626c4b3ff3445e2","tid":662850,"uid":125109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"首先利申 未試過宮崎自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔知你啲行李會點處理<br />\n<br />\n直覺上覺得day 2同day 3調轉會好啲<br />\n<br />\n指宿果邊如果唔自駕<br />\n而係搭巴士遊曬幾個景點<br />\n可能要10點幾就到指宿<br />\n如果第二日係宮崎去鹿兒島 再去指宿<br />\n唔知你啲交通配唔配合到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"感謝你既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地本身light package 所以應該handcarry <br />\n其實本身都想去宮崎，唔知大家推唔推薦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42638b94b93a5be7d0755bdd4567264ce0b7a979","tid":662850,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"指宿玉手箱 鹿兒島-&gt;指宿 尾班車好似12:00 定13:00 開"},{"pid":"316411d200597981de3130c3b472bdb3322dbbfa","tid":662850,"uid":163252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T21:40:13.000Z","msg":"樓主參加Cu 日研d programme <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fc4fb4b5bf7e899d2150cb3c88b9efe45581b6","tid":662850,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:52:12.000Z","msg":"好chur咁"},{"pid":"dd3e34c1fda1aa297ae8d7f2fcfad6069c1dc7a7","tid":662850,"uid":33733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:54:39.000Z","msg":"第一日就去高千穗<br />\n有啲chur<br />\n唔會去櫻島?"},{"pid":"49ed99c280083d0e8520d2ec2122cbf8425f2293","tid":662850,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"唔自駕去九州的話會浪費好多時間係交通<br />\n又要趕巴士miss左又要等一兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796cc2321130ed0fc768eb64837fc6660223d016","tid":662850,"uid":18220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"4日太短<br />\n我7日自駕遊遊曬霧島 &gt; 宮崎 &gt; 鹿兒島 &gt; 指宿<br />\n都覺得短<br />\n<br />\n高千穗我無去過但多人話伏<br />\n北少少我推介霧島アートの森<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/095244_ee405c04a24eed942af9068249b2c0a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F095244_ee405c04a24eed942af9068249b2c0a9.png&h=958f39cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/095245_d2ff4d32c844375058b9d5a61ca17cfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F095245_d2ff4d32c844375058b9d5a61ca17cfd.png&h=86e2591b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n神話之里公園必去，瀡滑梯好正<br />\n另外去指宿其實渣車係平過火車，當然火車好有特色，但要留意班次好疏<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/095426_98ab15d9996e2dc880db3f97639163f9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F095426_98ab15d9996e2dc880db3f97639163f9.png&h=b208a92a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd99affa06cc4403946f7eae7e66548176aeaeb5","tid":662850,"uid":3436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上面巴打講得岩 搭車都無半日<br />\nCut 指宿啦 其實都係熱砂浴 都夏天啦 坐係度都出汗 有咩意思 同埋要去食流水麵 龍宮神社果d 無車又要預時間搭巴士"},{"pid":"f173e7993a5aebf8a88cb05f6e749e43c580c2ef","tid":662850,"uid":79967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"鹿兒島有間Hotel Taisei Annex<br />\n平平地 近JR 附近又多好野食<br />\n男住客可以去大浴場 <br />\n(我覺得幾正，個feel有啲似日本打工仔四圍工幹 要過埋夜果隻)"},{"pid":"15787298e7b1ad751727f0cf58d9bf7a30ea0252","tid":662850,"uid":79967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd3e34c1fda1aa297ae8d7f2fcfad6069c1dc7a7","tid":662850,"uid":33733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:54:39.000Z","msg":"第一日就去高千穗<br />\n有啲chur<br />\n唔會去櫻島?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"櫻島正 有個位有幾隻貓貓蒲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" c